South Africa bids its final farewell to struggle stalwart Dr Andrew Mlangeni. Mlangeni died last week at the age of 95. Masego Rahlaga spoke to ANC NEC member Fikile Mbalula. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - South Africa bids its final farewell to struggle stalwart Dr Andrew Mlangeni. Mlangeni died last week at the age of 95. READ: ANC bids farewell to Andrew Mlangeni He's the last of the Rivonia trialists. Mlangeni will be laid to rest this Wednesday morning. 